From the balance sheet, I can see:
- Fixed Assets initial value: 8000000.00 on 2023-12-31
- Fixed Assets end value: 10670827.47 on 2024-02-05

These represent the tangible assets held by the company for operational purposes before accounting for accumulated depreciation.
